'''婴儿死亡率'''（{{lang-en|infant mortality rate}}，缩写为IMR）是指每1000名活产儿中在一岁前死亡的人口数<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Mathews TJ, MacDorman MF | title = Infant mortality statistics from the 2009 period linked birth/infant death data set | journal = National Vital Statistics Reports | volume = 61 | issue = 8 | pages = 1–27 | date = January 2013 | pmid = 24979974 | url = https://www.cdc.gov/nchs/data/nvsr/nvsr61/nvsr61_08.pdf | access-date = 2020-08-25 | archive-date = 2020-11-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201115121811/https://www.cdc.gov/nchs/data/nvsr/nvsr61/nvsr61_08.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Indicator Metadata Registry Details|url=https://www.who.int/data/maternal-newborn-child-adolescent/monitor|access-date=2020-07-29|website=www.who.int|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115104602/https://www.who.int/data/maternal-newborn-child-adolescent/monitor|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{Failed verification|reason=This is just a home page without information on IMR|date=August 2020}}。这个比率是衡量一个国家健康水平的指标。由于婴儿死亡率只统计一岁以下的数据， 而统计五岁以下儿童死亡的[[儿童死亡率|儿童死亡率]]也是一个重要的统计数据<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://data.unicef.org/topic/child-survival/under-five-mortality/|title=Under-Five Mortality|work=UNICEF|accessdate=2017-03-07|archive-date=2020-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200423234915/https://data.unicef.org/topic/child-survival/under-five-mortality/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2013年時，美國婴儿死亡死因的第一名是先天缺陷<ref name="pmid11837053">{{cite journal | vauthors = Mathews TJ, MacDorman MF, Menacker F | title = Infant mortality statistics from the 1999 period linked birth/infant death data set | journal = National Vital Statistics Reports | volume = 50 | issue = 4 | pages = 1–28 | date = January 2002 | pmid = 11837053 | doi = 10.1037/e558952006-001 | hdl = 1903/24216 | url = https://www.cdc.gov/nchs/data/nvsr/nvsr50/nvsr50_04.pdf | access-date = 2020-08-25 | archive-date = 2021-03-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210309182709/http://www.cdc.gov/nchs/data/nvsr/nvsr50/nvsr50_04.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>。其他的死因有{{le|出生窒息|birth asphyxia}}、[[肺炎|肺炎]]、[[先天性障碍|先天性障碍]]、足月分娩併發症（例如{{le|臍帶脫垂|Umbilical cord prolapse}}或是[[滯產|滯產]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.webmd.com/baby/understanding-labor-delivery-complications-basics#3|title=Labor and Delivery Complications -- the Basics|work=WebMD|access-date=2017-03-16|archive-date=2019-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190130091935/https://www.webmd.com/baby/understanding-labor-delivery-complications-basics#3|dead-url=no}}</ref>、{{le|新生兒感染|neonatal infection}}、[[腹瀉|腹瀉]]、[[疟疾|疟疾]]、[[麻疹|麻疹]]及[[營養不良|營養不良]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.womenandchildrenfirst.org.uk/infant-mortality-newborn-health |title=Infant Mortality & Newborn Health |publisher=Women and Children First |access-date=2017-04-25 |archive-date=2019-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210053014/https://www.womenandchildrenfirst.org.uk/infant-mortality-newborn-health |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 婴儿死亡死因中，最常見可預防的原因是孕婦在懷孕時吸煙<ref name=pmid27467563>{{cite journal | vauthors = Hall ES, Venkatesh M, Greenberg JM | s2cid = 29303225 | title = A population study of first and subsequent pregnancy smoking behaviors in Ohio | journal = Journal of Perinatology | volume = 36 | issue = 11 | pages = 948–953 | date = November 2016 | pmid = 27467563 | doi = 10.1038/jp.2016.119 }}</ref>。沒有產前檢查、孕婦在懷孕時飲酒或是管制藥物使用也可能會導致併發症，造成婴儿死亡<ref>{{Cite web|last=CDC|date=2020-06-03|title=Commit to Healthy Choices to Help Prevent Birth Defects {{!}} CDC|url=https://www.cdc.gov/ncbddd/birthdefects/prevention.html|access-date=2020-07-30|website=Centers for Disease Control and Prevention|language=en-us|archive-date=2021-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304222227/https://www.cdc.gov/ncbddd/birthdefects/prevention.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{Failed verification|reason=參考資料是有關避免一般性的先天缺陷，不是專指會造成新生兒死亡的先天缺陷|date=2020年8月}}。許多環境因素會影響婴儿死亡率，例如母親的教育程度、環境因素、政治以及醫療上的基礎建設<ref name=pmid26195213>{{cite journal | vauthors = Genowska A, Jamiołkowski J, Szafraniec K, Stepaniak U, Szpak A, Pająk A | title = Environmental and socio-economic determinants of infant mortality in Poland: an ecological study | journal = Environmental Health | volume = 14 | pages = 61 | date = July 2015 | pmid = 26195213 | pmc = 4508882 | doi = 10.1186/s12940-015-0048-1 }}</ref>。改善[[卫生设施|卫生设施]]、讓大家可以取得潔淨的飲用水、提昇對[[感染|感染性疾病]]的{{le|免疫|immunization}}，以及其他[[公共卫生|公共卫生]]措施都有助於降低婴儿死亡率。

2018年的报告给出的世界平均婴儿死亡率为千分之30。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=CHILD SURVIVAL: KEY FACTS AND FIGURES|author=UN Inter-agency Group for Child Mortality Estimation|url=https://childmortality.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/UN-IGME-Child-Mortality-Report-2018.pdf|journal=Levels & Trends in Child Mortality|issue=Report 2018|doi=|others=|year=2018|volume=|page=2|pmid=|access-date=2019-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200208183838/https://childmortality.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/UN-IGME-Child-Mortality-Report-2018.pdf|archive-date=2020-02-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 而五岁以下儿童死亡率为千分之39。 跟1990年相比已有很好的改善。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Levels and Trends in Child Mortality Report 2018 {{!}} United Nations Population Division {{!}} Department of Economic and Social Affairs|url=https://www.un.org/en/development/desa/population/publications/mortality/child-mortality-report-2018.asp|accessdate=2019-09-13|work=www.un.org|language=EN|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308155351/https://www.un.org/en/development/desa/population/publications/mortality/child-mortality-report-2018.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref>

